◆ APPEND_STMT

#define APPEND_STMT (   node)
Value:
if (!stmts_head) \
{ \
stmts_head = node; \
stmts_tail = node; \
} \
else \
{ \
stmts_tail->next = node; \
stmts_tail = node; \
}
